  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "So you advocate we \"patch\" the current widget to pass the issues we currently have and wait for the complete implementation of the instant search demo and a few other integrations (magento, wordpress, etc) to see how we can find a more generic way?\n\nWorks for me, as long as we don't officially release the hackish versions\n",
